te(seq)&lt;/span&gt;                   &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;←&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;释放&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;Block&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;       &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;│&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;       &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;▼&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;Tokenizer.decode([358,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;716&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;1664&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;  &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;&quot;I am fine.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;                                 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;←&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;返回给用户&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" id="53UOfJstDX-LK2dmV8hZ-1">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1370" width="560" x="2748" y="1260" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <mxCell id="53UOfJstDX-LK2dmV8hZ-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="完整的请求流程" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="60" x="2740.75" y="1240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="53UOfJstDX-LK2dmV8hZ-3" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;ol start=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; counter-reset: ol_list 0; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;推理引擎 = 调度 + 内存管理 + GPU 执行&lt;/strong&gt;，三者缺一不可&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;Block 是内存管理的基本单元&lt;/strong&gt;，把变长问题变成定长问题&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;Prefix Caching 是性能的杠杆&lt;/strong&gt;，xxhash + 引用计数 = 零成本复用&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;CUDA Graph 消除小批量开销&lt;/strong&gt;，让 decode 阶段不被 kernel launch 拖累&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;张量并行只需要 all_reduce&lt;/strong&gt;，每层 2 次通信足够&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;全局 Context 简化参数传递&lt;/strong&gt;，让深层模块无需关心调用链&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;Gumbel-Max 采样&lt;/strong&gt;比 multinomial 更高效且可融合编译&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="260" width="560" x="1800" y="35" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="53UOfJstDX-LK2dmV8hZ-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="本质" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="60" x="1790" y="25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="02qz6rVlwzZzbUxGRqx5-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="warmup 阶段的 prepare_prefill() 不是在准备真实请求，而是在构造一个“最大 prefill 形状”的假 batch，用来跑一次前向并测峰值显存。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="95" width="150" x="2350" y="385" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="02qz6rVlwzZzbUxGRqx5-3" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="Q 是本轮需要计算的新 token；&#xa;K/V 的可见长度是全 sequence 长度；&#xa;历史 K/V 来自 KV cache，新 token 的 K/V 在本轮计算并写入 cache。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="137" x="1989" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="02qz6rVlwzZzbUxGRqx5-6" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#333333;" value="更新&amp;nbsp;config.num_kvcache_blocks &amp;amp;&amp;amp; self.kv_cache" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="180" x="1646.25" y="760" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Vzc5gZPBLL40l2ow3U8Z-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="更新&amp;nbsp; seq.num_scheduled_tokens 本次调度 tokens 数量" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="200" x="1166" y="2349" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Vzc5gZPBLL40l2ow3U8Z-3" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;p style=&quot;--tw-space-y-reverse: 0; margin-block: 0px 16px; margin: 6px 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(36, 37, 41); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;支持的 prefill 场景：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;amp;]:pl-6&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;unordered-list&quot; style=&quot;--tw-space-y-reverse: 0; margin-block: 0px 16px; list-style-type: disc; white-space: normal; padding-left: 2em; display: flex !important; flex-direction: column !important; gap: 6px !important; margin: 6px 0px !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(36, 37, 41); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;普通 prefill&lt;/span&gt;：prompt 长度不超过剩余 token budget，整条 sequence 一次性 prefill 完，然后从&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;waiting&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;移到&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;running&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;batch prefill&lt;/span&gt;：多个短 prompt 可以在同一轮一起 prefill，只要满足&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;len(scheduled_seqs) &amp;lt; max_num_seqs&lt;/code&gt;，并且总 token 数不超过&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;md-inline-variable-like&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;max_num_batched_tokens&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;chunked prefill&lt;/span&gt;：如果 waiting 队首第一条 sequence 太长，超过本轮&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;remaining&lt;/code&gt;，允许只调度其中一段：&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;seq.num_scheduled_tokens = remaining&lt;/code&gt;。没 prefill 完的部分继续留在&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;waiting&lt;/code&gt;，下一次&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;step()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;接着处理。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;prefix cache / 已缓存 prefill&lt;/span&gt;：&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;num_tokens = seq.num_tokens - seq.num_cached_tokens&lt;/code&gt;，如果前面已有 token 被缓存，只调度未缓存的部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;KV cache 容量保护&lt;/span&gt;：新 sequence 如果还没&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;md-inline-variable-like&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;block_table&lt;/code&gt;，会先检查&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;can_allocate(seq)&lt;/code&gt;；KV block 不够就不调度，避免写 KV cache 越界。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;max sequence 数保护&lt;/span&gt;：本轮最多调度&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;md-inline-variable-like&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;max_num_seqs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;条 sequence，多余的留在&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;waiting&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;max batched token 数保护&lt;/span&gt;：本轮总 prefill token 数不会超过&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;md-inline-variable-like&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;max_num_batched_tokens&lt;/code&gt;，通过&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;remaining&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;和&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;min(num_tokens, remaining)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;保证。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;--tw-space-y-reverse: 0; margin-block: 0px 16px; margin: 6px 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(36, 37, 41); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;不支持/有意限制的场景：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;amp;]:pl-6&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;unordered-list&quot; style=&quot;--tw-space-y-reverse: 0; margin-block: 0px 16px; list-style-type: disc; white-space: normal; padding-left: 2em; display: flex !important; flex-direction: column !important; gap: 6px !important; margin: 6px 0px !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(36, 37, 41); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;非队首 sequence 的 chunked prefill&lt;/span&gt;：如果本轮已经调度了一些 seq，下一条放不下，不会把它切一小段塞进去，而是直接&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;break&lt;/code&gt;，留到下一轮。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-semibold&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;strong&quot; style=&quot;--tw-font-weight: 600; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;KV block 不够时继续抢占 running&lt;/span&gt;：prefill 阶段 block 不够就停；抢占逻辑主要在 decode 阶段&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;preempt()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;里。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 6px 0px 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(36, 37, 41); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;一句话：这段 prefill 支持“多个短请求合批”和“队首长请求分块”，但不会为了填满剩余 token budget 去切后面的请求。&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="480" width="560" y="2232" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
