        <mxCell id="6CuZw47QnxaL8d48UyvQ-44" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;ul class=&quot;list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;amp;]:pl-6&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;unordered-list&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; white-space: normal; padding-left: 2em; display: flex !important; flex-direction: column !important; gap: 6px !important; margin: 6px 0px 0px !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(36, 37, 41); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;多卡情况下，先判断输入 token 哪些属于当前 rank 的词表范围。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;对属于当前 rank 的 token，把全局 token id 转成当前分片里的局部 id。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;用本地分片权重做&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;md-inline-path-filename-like&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;md-inline-path-filename&quot;&gt;F.embedding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;不属于当前 rank 的位置会被 mask 成 0。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;py-1 [&amp;amp;&amp;gt;p]:inline&quot; data-streamdown=&quot;list-item&quot; style=&quot;padding-block: 4px; word-break: break-word; padding: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;最后&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;padding: 1.5px 4px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.08); color: color(srgb 1 1 1 / 0.94); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;dist.all_reduce(y)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;把所有 rank 的结果相加，得到完整 embedding 输出。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
