        <mxCell id="LEf6z_7qajuvW0js5KtZ-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.75;&quot;&gt;注意：采样参数是&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;拆分存储&lt;/strong&gt;而非保存整个 SamplingParams 对象，这样便于序列化传输（多进程通信时减少开销）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.75;&quot;&gt;关键设计：block_table 是一个整数列表，每个元素是一个 Block 的物理 ID。通过这张表，一个逻辑上连续的 token 序列被映射到了 GPU 上可能不连续的内存块。这就是 PagedAttention 的核心：&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;逻辑连续、物理分散&lt;/strong&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="560" x="1020" y="778" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="v3NVO1dQZbPmK4_CbLYU-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;pre class=&quot;syl-page-code&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 18px; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 15px; border: 0px; background: rgb(250, 250, 250); white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: block; overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 3px; text-align: left; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); box-shadow: rgba(216, 216, 216, 0.5) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs less&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-x: auto; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;ModelRunner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-class&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;.run&lt;/span&gt;() 被调用&#xa;    │&#xa;    ├── &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;prepare_prefill&lt;/span&gt;() 或 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;prepare_decode&lt;/span&gt;()&#xa;    │       └── &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;set_context&lt;/span&gt;(...)  ← 设置上下文&#xa;    │&#xa;    ├── &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;model&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-class&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;.forward&lt;/span&gt;()&#xa;    │       └── &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;Attention&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-class&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;.forward&lt;/span&gt;()&#xa;    │               └── &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;get_context&lt;/span&gt;()  ← 获取上下文&#xa;    │&#xa;    └── &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-selector-tag&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;reset_context&lt;/span&gt;()  ← 清理上下文&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="330" width="360" x="54" y="1990" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <UserObject label="&lt;pre class=&quot;syl-page-code&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 18px; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 15px; border: 0px; background: rgb(250, 250, 250); white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: block; overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 3px; text-align: left; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); box-shadow: rgba(216, 216, 216, 0.5) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs python&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-x: auto; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# utils/context.py&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-meta&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;@dataclass&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-class&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;Context&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    is_prefill: bool = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 当前是 prefill 还是 decode&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    cu_seqlens_q: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Query 的累积序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    cu_seqlens_k: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Key 的累积序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    max_seqlen_q: int = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;                 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 最长 Query 序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    max_seqlen_k: int = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;                 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 最长 Key 序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    slot_mapping: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Token → KV Cache 物理位置&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    context_lens: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Decode 时各序列的上下文长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    block_tables: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 各序列的 Block 表&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&#xa;_CONTEXT = Context()  &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 全局单例&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-function&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;get_context&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-params&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; _CONTEXT&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-function&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;set_context&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-params&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;(...)&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;global&lt;/span&gt; _CONTEXT; _CONTEXT = Context(...)&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-function&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;reset_context&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-params&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;global&lt;/span&gt; _CONTEXT; _CONTEXT = Context()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" link="&lt;pre class=&quot;syl-page-code&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 18px; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 15px; border: 0px; background: rgb(250, 250, 250); white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: block; overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 3px; text-align: left; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); box-shadow: rgba(216, 216, 216, 0.5) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs python&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-x: auto; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# utils/context.py&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-meta&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 117, 59);&quot;&gt;@dataclass&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-class&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;Context&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    is_prefill: bool = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 当前是 prefill 还是 decode&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    cu_seqlens_q: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Query 的累积序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    cu_seqlens_k: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Key 的累积序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    max_seqlen_q: int = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;                 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 最长 Query 序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    max_seqlen_k: int = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;                 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 最长 Key 序列长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    slot_mapping: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Token → KV Cache 物理位置&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    context_lens: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# Decode 时各序列的上下文长度&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;    block_tables: torch.Tensor = &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-literal&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 各序列的 Block 表&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&#xa;_CONTEXT = Context()  &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;# 全局单例&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-function&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(168, 46, 46);&quot;&gt;get_context&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-params&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(17, 75, 166);&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; _CONTEXT&#xa;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-function&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(138, 115, 4);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; sty